# Inject an actuator fault into the live simulation.
# thruster_id: 1..4 (paper's u1..u4)
# fault_factor: 0.0 = total loss, 1.0 = fully healthy
# fault_type: "abrupt" | "slow" (slow = linear ramp over 'ramp_seconds')
# ramp_seconds: time to interpolate from healthy to fault_factor (ignored if abrupt)
int32    thruster_id
float64  fault_factor
string   fault_type
float64  ramp_seconds
---
bool     accepted
string   message
